OL,3,CEx-reporter warned he could face
OL,4,Cprison for harassing four victims
OL,6,FA former journalist has been told he
OL,7,Fcould face a prison sentence for
OL,8,Fharassing four victims.
OL,10,FRobert Sutcliffe, 58, appeared at
OL,11,FLeeds Magistrates' Court on Wednesday
OL,12,Fafter admitting five charges of
OL,13,Fharassment without violence.
OL,15,FSutcliffe, of Edgerton Road in
OL,16,FHuddersfield, was due to be sentenced
OL,17,Fin November last year, but the case
OL,18,Fwas moved to Leeds Magistrates' Court,
OL,19,Fwhere he appeared on Wednesday.
