OL,3,CEx-reporter warned he could face
OL,4,Cprison for harassing four victims
OL,6,FHe spoke to confirm his date of birth
OL,7,Fand address before the case was again
OL,8,Fadjourned, until 20 March.
OL,10,FSutcliffe, a former Bradford Telegraph
OL,11,Fand Argus and Yorkshire Post reporter,
OL,12,Fleft his most recent job for the Reach
OL,13,Fwebsite Yorkshire Live last year after
OL,14,Fbeing suspended.
OL,16,FCourt documents show the charges
OL,17,Frelate to four different victims. The
OL,18,Ffirst offence relates to unwanted
OL,19,Fmessages and posts on social media
OL,20,Fcausing the victim to feel harassed,
OL,21,Falarmed and distressed.
