OL,6,FShe said: "Clearly imprisonment is
OL,7,Fvery much a possibility in this case.
OL,8,FTwo of the matters fall to be in
OL,9,Fcategory A1 - and towards the top in
OL,10,Frelation to (a victim.)
OL,12,F"In these circumstances it does need
OL,13,Fto be dealt with carefully."
OL,15,FThe judge said the prosecution had not
OL,16,Fhad the opportunity to assess the
OL,17,F"lengthy victim impact statements".
